To create a discord bot that automates commands with the Myuu pokemon bot, you can use discord.js, which is a powerful Node.js module that allows you to interact with the Discord API. Here are the following steps that can be followed to create and automate commands with the Myuu pokemon bot:

1. SET UP A NEW BOT: Create a new discord bot to handle the commands. Create the bot account, get the bot token and add it to your discord server.

2. INSTALL DISCORD.JS: Install the discord.js package using npm by running the following command in the terminal: 

```
npm install discord.js
```

3. CONNECT THE DISCORD BOT TO SERVER: Connect the bot to the Discord server using the bot token generated above:

```js
const Discord = require('discord.js');
const client = new Discord.Client();
client.login('bot_token_here'); // Replace bot_token_here with your own bot token
```

4. SET UP COMMAND HANDLING: Set up the command handling system to listen for and respond to user commands. When a user sends a message with a specific command prefix, such as '!' or '?', the bot will check the command and execute accordingly.

```js
client.on('message', (message) => {
    if (message.content.startsWith('!myuu')) {
        const args = message.content.slice(5).trim().split(/ +/);
        const command = args.shift().toLowerCase();

        // Handle the commands
        if (command === 'catch') {
            // Automate the catch command with the Myuu bot
        } else if (command === 'spawn') {
            // Automate the spawn command with the Myuu bot
        }
    }
});
```

5. AUTOMATE THE MYUU POKEMON BOT COMMANDS: Automate the Myuu Pokemon bot commands using the `message.channel.send()` method and the Myuu Pokemon bot command prefixes to trigger the commands. The prefixes can be determined using the !help command in the Myuu Pokemon bot.

```js
client.on('message', (message) => {
    if (message.content.startsWith('!myuu')) {
        const args = message.content.slice(5).trim().split(/ +/);
        const command = args.shift().toLowerCase();

        // Handle the commands
        if (command === 'catch') {
            message.channel.send('p!catch ' + args.join(' ')); // Automates the catch command with the Myuu bot
        } else if (command === 'spawn') {
            message.channel.send('p!spawn ' + args.join(' ')); // Automates the spawn command with the Myuu bot
        }
    }
});
```

6. RUN THE BOT: Save the code and start the bot using `node bot.js` (assuming the name of your code file is `bot.js`).

Overall, this will allow the creation of a Discord bot that can automate the commands with the Myuu Pokemon bot to make it more convenient for users to catch and spawn pokemon without the need for manual inputs.
